<p>Given:</p>
<pre><code><span><span class="mtk1">A&nbsp;=&nbsp;[[1,&nbsp;2],&nbsp;[3,&nbsp;4]]</span></span><br><span><span class="mtk1">B&nbsp;=&nbsp;[[5,&nbsp;6],&nbsp;[7,&nbsp;8]]</span></span>
</code></pre><ol>
<li>Compute <strong>element-wise product</strong> <code>C = A * B</code></li>
<li>Compute <strong>matrix multiplication</strong> <code>D = A @ B</code></li>
<li>Compute the <strong>dot product</strong> of vectors <code>[1,2,3]</code> and <code>[4,5,6]</code> → <code>dp</code></li>
<li>Multiply all elements of <code>A</code> by scalar 3 → <code>E</code></li>
</ol>
</span></div>
