<li>Compute <code>P + Q</code> (matrix addition)</li>
<li>Compute <code>3 * P</code> (scalar multiplication)</li>
<li>Compute <code>P @ Q</code> (matrix multiplication)</li>
<li>Verify that matrix multiplication is <strong>not commutative</strong> — show <code>P @ Q ≠ Q @ P</code>.</li>
</ol>
