<p>A bag contains: 4 red, 3 blue, 3 green marbles.</p>
<ol>
<li>Define the sample space and compute P(red), P(blue), P(green).</li>
<li>Two marbles drawn <strong>without replacement</strong>. Compute:<ul>
<li>P(first=red, second=blue) — <strong>joint probability</strong></li>
<li>P(second=blue | first=red) — <strong>conditional probability</strong></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Are the two draws <strong>independent</strong>? Show mathematically.</li>
</ol>
</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

